        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 4 at 11:02PM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 1102 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 15
miles south of Garden City, moving northeast at 60 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 40 mph and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
Saint Lawrence and Garden City.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
